thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Gina Wittingslow

author: Gina Wittingslow
title: Gina Wittingslow
text: I recently purchased my first home and had heard not to trust Real estate agents but Truc, whom it met at both viewing of the property and at the auction was very pleasant to deal with. She was honest and caring and made the experience a great one. She even took pictures of us putting on the sold sticker and sent the photos!!
